                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                            <locus from="1r"/>
                            <title type="complete">Collection of Psalter excerpts and malkǝʾ-hymns</title>
                            
                            <note>Though the manuscript is called <foreign xml:lang="gez">Gubāʾe malk</foreign> in <ref target="#a1"/>, 
                                it differs from most known witnesses of this work by containing psalms and comparatively few <foreign xml:lang="gez">malkǝʾ</foreign>-hymns. </note>
                            
